            "type": "text",
            "data": "Setup Reports"
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "image4304.gif",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Report Groups may be created to contain Reports that are similar to each other OR Report Groups could be created to contain all Reports needed for a certain type of Job."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Creating a Report Group"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "When you click Setup Reports, you will see the following screen:"
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "Setup_Reports_1.png",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "This is a list of the Advanced Bid Reports that are available in CABINET VISION. In the sidebar is a list of all of the Report Groups that have been created.  To create a new report group, simply click the Add button  and then enter the name that you want to use for this group. When you click OK the new group will be added to the list of Report Groups."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "After you have created your new Report Group, you will need to begin assigning Reports to that Group. To add a Report to a Group, click on that Report and then click the check box to add a check next to the desired Report Group. As you scroll down the right side of your screen you will notice that some of the Reports have a green CV icon in front of them. This green CV icon lets you know that the Report has been assigned to a Group. If you click on that Report you will see a check mark next to one or more of the Report \"Groups\" in the sidebar. Reports can be assigned to more than one group if you like."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Report List area"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "/   Adding a Report to a Group"
        },
        {
