            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "To add a Report to a Group click on the Report you would like to add to a Group, so that it is highlighted. Then in the \"Groups\" window click on the check box next to the name of the Group you would like to add the highlighted Report to. Once added the Report icon will either be   or  ."
